arts.ttl: Villa's Carlos joins Fenerbahce on 3½-year deal
arts.sum: Aston Villa defender Diego Carlos has joined Fenerbahce on a 3½-year deal, the Turkish Super Lig side said on Thursday.

arts.ttl: Crystal Palace legend Wilfried Zaha ends Lyon spell to join MLS side
arts.sum: Zaha made 458 appearances for the Eagles and is the club’s record Premier League goalscorer. Ex-Crystal Palace winger Wilfried Zaha has joined MLS side Charlotte FC on loan until January 2026.

arts.ttl: Carlos leaves Villa to join Fenerbahce
arts.sum: Turkish side Fenerbahce sign defender Diego Carlos from Aston Villa for an undisclosed fee.

Aston Villa can confirm that Diego Carlos has joined Fenerbahçe for an undisclosed fee. The defender played his last match on December 30 vs Brighton. He signed for Villa in the summer of 2022, joining from Sevilla and made 58 appearances in 3 seasons in claret and blue. Aston Villa Football Club would like to wish Diego good luck in his new professional chapter.

arts.ttl: Real break 1bn euro barrier to top money league
arts.sum: Real Madrid become the first football club to generate more than 1bn euros in annual revenue, according to analysis by Deloitte.
